Uses of Class
opennlp.ccg.hylo.graph.LFEdge

Packages that use LFEdge
opennlp.ccg.disjunctivizer Package for the disjunctivizer, which creates a disjunctive LF XML structure based on an LFGraphDifference. 
opennlp.ccg.hylo.graph Provides representations of LFs as traversible graphs based on the JGraphT package, as well as customized filters for sets of edges in those graphs.
